{"tid":2000859,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港殯儀館冧8米假天花  連吊燈跌落大堂 幸無人行經","createTime":"2020-05-04T06:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T07:28:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2b5a0729bd77174efbb95dcec0619219ece1d146","tid":2000859,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:47:13.000Z","msg":"全文 link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200504/576SQ4EUGUFAA4CMRZU5SWAKPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200504%2F576SQ4EUGUFAA4CMRZU5SWAKPY%2F&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX9gc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=6f43925c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200504%2F576SQ4EUGUFAA4CMRZU5SWAKPY%2F&h=b4b71068\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200504/576SQ4EUGUFAA4CMRZU5SWAKPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港殯儀館冧8米假天花 <br />\n連吊燈跌落大堂 幸無人行經<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200504/large/1588523463_dcdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200504%2Flarge%2F1588523463_dcdb.jpg&h=a4840ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨晨香港殯儀館一幅巨型假天花板連鐵架直墮大堂。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】俗稱香港大酒店、落成逾半世紀的香港殯儀館，昨晨發生驚險塌天花板意外，地下大堂一幅巨型假天花板懷疑日。。。。。。。。<br />\n虞。意外中無人受傷，事後殯儀館召工人清理塌下的假天花板，昨晚地下靈堂的喪事如常舉行。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄭大康<br />\n<br />\n香港殯儀館位於北角英皇道679號，地下大堂有三幅假天花板，塌下的為中。。。。。。。。<br />\n大吊燈。殯儀館地下設有兩個靈堂，接待處設在大堂近牆邊位置。<br />\n<br />\n晚上喪禮繼續舉行<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事發在昨日上午，該幅假天花板突然連同吊燈塌落地下大堂，地面滿佈瓦礫，幸好事發時大堂無人，假天花塌下的位置。。。。。。。。<br />\n者提供的相片顯示，塌下的假天花支架有鐵銹迹，一條疑連着吊燈的電線半空垂下。<br />\n<br />\n記者晚上到現場視察，發現大堂已清理乾淨，但塌下的假天花位置，仍可見六個相信用作固定假天花的釘痕，釘痕附近有。。。。。。。。。<br />\n擺放有一棵巨型盆栽，相當突兀，懷疑是事故令地磚破裂，殯儀館擺放盆栽遮蔽。<br />\n<br />\n昨殯儀館喪事未有受事件影響，地下兩個靈堂其中一個靈堂仍。。。。。。。。<br />\n有報警。記者問殯儀館職員，職員表示不清楚，只知是早上的事情。<br />\n<br />\n座落於北角的香港殯儀館，是香港島目前唯一的殯儀館，1966年9月建成，全館共有20個大小禮堂，其中位於一樓的「基恩。。。。。。。。<br />\n館收費較高，但交通方便，且不少名人富豪均居於港島區，故成為城中名人富豪之喪禮首選。"},{"pid":"a58ec8fc262cf475c6eeabd52d06849d0988dda6","tid":2000859,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"咁猛"},{"pid":"23e5694d9aca122cfc813757d8de4c5540c1abd6","tid":2000859,"uid":48582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d3f256b82b891b0ef9c05893e715dce82be6b4b7","tid":2000859,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:49:59.000Z","msg":"中左既話可以即刻開埋個堂"},{"pid":"28459c5aebd04fa519bdc82d6472e05c1e09a79a","tid":2000859,"uid":62721,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"壓到人又多一單生意做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c976d331a15464a6527b855f1eb3932c669fbd","tid":2000859,"uid":157304,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"或者我 已不會存在⋯⋯"},{"pid":"3f854333656479ed872898a6bd75da77815ea1c6","tid":2000859,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28459c5aebd04fa519bdc82d6472e05c1e09a79a","tid":2000859,"uid":62721,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"壓到人又多一單生意做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"車都慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd79846b1a0694e3e35a431288ea39dc1292a48e","tid":2000859,"uid":51057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"睇錯連登跌落大堂.."},{"pid":"ba0af6ff0adcbbd4299391a430a6cd3401dd1a14","tid":2000859,"uid":197441,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:57:04.000Z","msg":"手足。。"},{"pid":"97128c1268a1e41c04ac4a08e04c4645d0decd8e","tid":2000859,"uid":145730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"若這一束吊燈傾瀉下來..."},{"